    "In other words, this score can be transformed into a percentage where 0 is 0% while 1 is 100%.",
    "For the latency, we use the seconds as the scale.",
    "This study used three common set separations i.e., the training set, validation set, and testing set.",
    "In the first stage, the dataset was divided into two parts: the training set and the testing set.",
    "The validation set was taken from the training set through K-fold cross-validation."
